Class LND1Function

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.LND1Function
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, FunctionIntf

    public class LND1Function
extends java.lang.Object
implements FunctionIntf
    class implements the so-called LND1 function (continuous, non-differentiable). Its global minimum value for any number of dimensions is zero. The function is a "generalization" of MAXQ problem. See Haarala (2004) and Brimberg et al (2013).

    Title: popt4jlib

    Description: A Parallel Meta-Heuristic Optimization Library in Java
